{"title":"Parental bereavement leave","public_updated_at":"2017-04-11T10:16:24Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This consultation seeks your views on the proposal to introduce statutory Parental Bereavement Leave and Pay for employed parents who lose a child.</p>\n\n<p>There is currently no specific parental entitlement to time off work (paid or otherwise) following the death of a child and the Government wants to ensure that all employed parents have the opportunity to have time away from the workplace to grieve for a lost child.</p>\n</div>","closing_date":"2017-05-16T23:45:00.000+01:00","emphasised_organisations":["2bde479a-97f2-42b5-986a-287a623c2a1c"],"opening_date":"2017-04-18T09:30:00.000+01:00","ways_to_respond":{"email":"labourmarket.consultations@beis.gov.uk","link_url":"https://beisgovuk.citizenspace.com/lm/parental-bereavement-leave  ","postal_address":"Labour Market Directorate\r\nDepartment for Business, Energy and Industrial Strategy\r\n1 Victoria Street,\r\nLondon,\r\nSW1H 0ET"},"first_public_at":"2017-04-11T11:14:33.000+01:00","political":false,"government":{"title":"2015 Conservative government","slug":"2015-conservative-government","current":true},"tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":["labour-market-reform"],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/consultations/parental-bereavement-leave","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"open_consultation","schema_name":"consultation","first_published_at":null,"base_path":"/government/consultations/parental-bereavement-leave","description":"This consultation seeks your views on the proposal to introduce statutory parental bereavement leave and pay for employed parents who lose a child.  ","content_id":"ca19a6b2-3343-425e-8676-b3f4b89df76a","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1198","api_path":"/api/content/government/or